### ==========================================
### SUMMARY REPORT
### ==========================================
###
### ✅ Working Endpoints:
### - Health check
### - Authentication (register, login)
### - User management (list, get, update)
### - Address management (list, create, update, set default)
### - Category management
### - Product management
### - Cart management (add, update, remove, clear)
### - Order listing
### - Payment listing
### - AR listing
###
### ❌ Expected Failures:
### - Customer access to admin-only endpoints (403)
### - Without token (401)
###
### ⏭️ Skipped:
### - Delete operations (will break flow)
### - Order creation (needs pre-setup)
### - Some operations requiring existing data
